name: MODDM3 REJECTS
description: Well, after not working on moddm3 in a LONG freaking time, I looked at it and decided that out of 3.2349 maps, I only liked 1. I kept map02, scrapped map04, but I liked map01 and map03 so much I decided to release them standalone. Please do not take this as a moddm3 demo version. Anyways,
